snippet.title: Leilani's Island Gameplay
snippet.description:
Available to wishilist now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/664640/Leilanis_Island/

Work in progress gameplay footage of Leilani's Island, a 2D platformer in the making for PC. Leilani has got to jump, roll, and smash things to take back her island from mechanical invasion!

Featuring music by Leila 'Woofle' Wilson: https://soundcloud.com/leila-wilson-woofle

For the latest info on the game please follow me on Twitter! https://twitter.com/ishisoft
